org.openimaj.hadoop.sequencefile

Class ExtractionState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.hadoop.sequencefile.ExtractionState

  • public class ExtractionState
extends Object
    The state describing the extraction process from SequenceFile. Basically, this class stores the current state of the extraction and determines whether the next item should be extracted or not.
    Author:
    Sina Samangooei (ss@ecs.soton.ac.uk), Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
